      <div class="col-lg-8 col-md-6 to">
        <h2>PENTAGRAM</h2>
        <p>Welcome fellow Maths Nerds, lets make Maths fun :p</p>
      <hr>
      <p class="p3text" style="text-align: justify; padding-top: 40px;">
        Pentagram as a clubs is not just limited to maths but fun- filled events and activities giving students from different departments a platform to socialize and work together. The club conducted six succesful events in the previous semester

        The first three events of the semester were held over 5 days during Utsav-Envisage 22, namely, Infinite Amaze. Battle of Brains, and Under the Hammer All the 3 events were not only home-full but successful as well. After this, the club conducted its 2nd Recruitment Drive for the freshers, where about 70 students where fetched based on their skills and aptitude
                <br><br>
                Following this, Last Clan Standing, an event held in collaboration with IEEE PES was held on 23rd June, the event was open to all and gave the club freshers a chance to organize and manage the event entirely On account of WIE Day. Pentagrain in collaboration with IEEE WIE hosted PseudoMaths, an event based on nostalgic board & dice-based games with a touch of Maths this was one of the most successful events wherein participants turned up beyond expectations. Last but not least, Chaotic Detectives, an independent event based on a murder mystery was held on 3rd September, and the winners were awarded cash prizes.
              </div>
